- Yes, I was named Keerti.

00:26:07.170 --> 00:26:09.400
My father used to
call me, [INAUDIBLE]..

00:26:09.400 --> 00:26:14.450
You see, [INAUDIBLE] My father
believed in all religions.

00:26:14.450 --> 00:26:21.820
My sister who was older
to me, [INAUDIBLE] We

